snippet.title: Corsarios (Opera Soft) (1989) (Amstrad CPC)
snippet.description:
(See all text for Engish)
Injugable de la leche e injusto con el jugador, lo más rescatable de este "Corsarios" son sus gráficos. Es como un hermano pobre del Skull & Crossbones (que tampoco era una maravilla en ordenador).

Unplayable and unfair to the player, the most redeemable of "Corsarios" are its graphics. It's like a poor brother of Skull & Crossbones arcade (which its very standard conversion to computer).
